PQMT:




PQMT is a one stop shopping with intergrated tool sets which keep track of Plant data, PQMT, CAR, Scorecards, IMT, Best Practices.




Features: 




·        It has dashboard by business, product lines, product grouping.  




·        Integration to GEE QMS.  




·        Qualitymanagement tool that provides the reporting functions easily 




·        Mature system customizable to changing business needs. 




·        Standarized reporting in every plant.

