Hi

Pick-Pack Ship:




This application is used for




a)       Tracking picked items from Lift storage system




b)      Tracking shipments through RFID verification




c)       Tracking packing prediction for all orders




d)      Capturing any feedbacks for any item.




Digital Bins:




This application is basically for :




Tracking quantity of  items (nut/screw/bolt) at a particular rack. To provide a dashboard where the items quantity data from scales are been showed to the user and if the quantity reach below a threshold an alert is been triggered.




Dock To Stock:




   This application is implemented to overcome following challenges:




a)       Get clear visibility in receiving docks on what, when and how much.




b)      Provide good visibility on dock arrival and provide buyer to select slot reservation time

